        <p id="desktop-intro">
          What is a <span class="green-text">green system</span>? <br />
          - It is a future of sustainable energy! The concept of using
          materials, energy, water that enhances the airflow/efficiency within a
          system.
        </p>

        <img id="plant-image" src="/images/plant.png" alt="Plant" />
      </div>
      <div id="landing-section-2">
        <p id="desktop-overview">
          How will <span class="green-text">Greenflow</span> help you? <br />
